    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 1,
      "id": "frame4-tree",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 1120,
      "width": 500,
      "height": 250,
      "text": ".claude/skills/\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ linkedin-engagement-scraper/\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ SKILL.md\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ company-enrichment/\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ SKILL.md\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ contact-enrichment/\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ SKILL.md\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ lead-qualifier/\nв”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ SKILL.md\nв”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ config/\nв”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ scoring_rubric.md  вҶҗ Customize!\nв”Ӯ       в””в”Җв”Җ disqualifiers.md   вҶҗ Customize!\nв””в”Җв”Җ outreach-campaign/\n    в”ңв”Җв”Җ SKILL.md\n    в””в”Җв”Җ templates/\n        в””в”Җв”Җ sequences.md       вҶҗ Customize!",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": ["frame4"],
      "seed": 12
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "version": 1,
      "id": "frame4-flow",
      "x": 600,
      "y": 1120,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "How it works:\n\n  You say: \"qualify these leads\"\n       вҶ“\n  Claude reads: lead-qualifier/SKILL.md\n       вҶ“\n  Loads config: scoring_rubric.md + disqualifiers.md\n       вҶ“\n  Executes: 7-gate pipeline step by step\n       вҶ“\n  Outputs: ./output/qualified_*.json\n       вҶ“\n  You say: \"launch a campaign for hot leads\"\n       вҶ“\n  Claude reads: outreach-campaign/SKILL.md\n       вҶ“\n  ...and the chain continues",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#9c36b5",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": ["frame4"],
      "seed": 13
    },
    {
